msgstr "splat"

#: ../../S/splat.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../S/splat.rst:10
msgid ""
"Name used in many places (DEC, IBM, and others) for the asterisk (``*``\\) "
"character (ASCII 0101010). This may derive from the ‘squashed-bug’ "
"appearance of the asterisk on many early line printers."
msgstr ""
"アスタリスク(\\ ``*``\\ )文字(ASCII "
"0101010)を指して、多くの場所(DEC、IBMなど)で使われる名前。これはおそらく、多くの初期のラインプリンタでのアスタリスクの‘押しつぶされた虫’のような見た目に由来する。"

#: ../../S/splat.rst:14
msgid ""
"[MIT] Name used by some people for the ``#`` character (ASCII 0100011)."
msgstr "[MIT] ``#``\\ 文字(ASCII 0100011)を指して一部の人々が使う名前。"

#: ../../S/splat.rst:17
msgid "The :ref:`feature-key` on a Mac (same as :ref:`alt`\\, sense 2)."
msgstr "Macの\\ :ref:`feature-key`\\ (\\ :ref:`alt`\\ 、語義2と同じ)。"

#: ../../S/splat.rst:19
msgid ""
"obs. Name used by some people for the Stanford/ITS extended ASCII ⊗ "
"character. This character is also called blobby and frob, among other names;"
" it is sometimes used by mathematicians as a notation for tensor product."
msgstr ""
"廃語 "
"Stanford/ITSの拡張ASCIIの⊗文字を指して一部の人々が使う名前。この文字はblobbyやfrobなどとも呼ばれる。数学者がテンソル積の記法として使うこともある。"

#: ../../S/splat.rst:23
msgid ""
"obs. Name for the semi-mythical Stanford extended ASCII ⊕ character. See "
"also :ref:`ASCII`\\."
msgstr "廃語 半ば神話的なStanfordの拡張ASCIIの⊕文字の名前。\\ :ref:`ASCII`\\ も参照。"
